No. —, Original.

Ex parte : In the Matter of James Hamilton Lewis, Petitioner. Submitted May 21, 1906. Decided May 28, 1906. Per Curiam.

Motion for leave to file a petition for a writ of certiorari denied. Jones v. Montague, *615194 U. S. 147; Security Insurance Company v. Prewitt, 200 U. S. 446; Mills v. Green, 159 U. S. 651; Bessette v. W. B. Conkey Company, 194 U. S. 324.

Mr. Holmes Conrad for petitioner.
